r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpsyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=140b08fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpsyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=cf30e5b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"9bebe70f080ce4ec2c3849d06621a25b07757c8d","tid":1449784,"uid":34063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:19:42.000Z","msg":"邊個話我哋輸緊嘅我屌晒你哋老母！要嬴嘅全部同我入嚟！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dBbvRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dBbvRS</a><br />\n<br />\n推,所有掟磚同火魔法都係黑警扮示威者做既<br />\n緊記要事：<br />\n1. 射頭<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 室內射tear gas<br />\n5.一米同胡椒球對人發射<br />\n6.罔顧安全,推人落電梯<br />\n7.黑警插贓嫁禍,塞管狀物體入示威者背囊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POs3Lz7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOs3Lz7.jpg&h=6417b1c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7226a246109031cba41d4de34b3d86f80fb35836","tid":1449784,"uid":7580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"唔好塞鐵喇 學樓上話齋播片仲好"},{"pid":"2e580ac721c88529585ef1f8f181994c1fd403d2","tid":1449784,"uid":294930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:21:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣盡量以事實Facebook片，證據為主，<br />\n<br />\n真實暴露班狗嘅邢悪！</span></span>"},{"pid":"444cd4e5568d8372668d5e81c3eebfe52ccaadab","tid":1449784,"uid":41525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:22:35.000Z","msg":"唔洗，入地鐵不斷話有毒氣已經夠"},{"pid":"58e467ed25164d57b351d5ca6a152632eb330279","tid":1449784,"uid":15747,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:23:12.000Z","msg":"要佔就佔左條青馬佢<br />\n塞左主要幹線先係癱瘓機場最佳方法<br />\n係，係無得走無路可退<br />\n今晚班手足係尖咀葵芳太古佢地又有得退咩？<br />\n你覺得